## Repository structure

```text
epiprofile-plants/
├── src/
│   ├── core/      # core EpiProfile logic (adapted from EpiProfile 2.0)
│   ├── plants/    # plant-specific init_histone0_* and panel definitions
│   ├── qc/        # quality control and reporting utilities
│   └── utils/     # shared helper functions
├── layouts/       # tabular catalogs of histone peptides and panels
├── examples/
│   └── ONTOGENY_DEMO/   # minimal BOT/FLOR/SEN demo dataset (no raw WIFF)
├── docs/          # additional documentation (architecture, usage, design notes)
├── .github/workflows/   # optional CI workflows
├── LICENSE
└── README.md
